expression = re.compile(rfc._MONTH_REGEX)
bad_months = ['January', 'February', 'March', 'April', 'June', 'July',
    'August', 'September', 'October', 'November', 'December', 'Abc', 'Ja', '']
for bad_month in bad_months:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_month)), msg=
        "Bad Month Encoding '{m}' was matched and shouldn't have been".
        format(m=bad_month))
